activities:
ERM is a subsidiary of ERM Worldwide Limited. ERM Worldwide Limited and its worldwide affiliates provides environmental, health, safety, risk and social consulting services for their clients.

ERM and its subsidiaries, affiliates receive information from ERM group companies located in the EU/EEA and/or Switzerland, including organization, customer, supplier and employee data. The data transferred from the EU/EEA and/or Switzerland to the US is used for the following  non-exhaustive purposes:  
(i) business planning and workforce management;
(ii) monitoring employee performance, management, professional development and succession planning;
(iii) for the administration of employee payroll and benefits;
(iv) building and managing external relationships;
(v) knowledge management and sharing; 
(vi) promotion and provision of professional services.
